<li><a href="/wiki/E_programming_language" title="E programming language" class="mw-redirect">E</a>, a programming language based around capability security (<a href="http://www.erights.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.erights.org/" rel="nofollow">ERights.org</a>)</li>
